{"article_id":"2DYRi7fyH4rhPkTa","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Supreme Court nominee Judge Brett Kavanaugh at his Senate Judiciary Committee confirmation hearing , September 4 , 2018 .","depth":3},{"id":1,"text":"( Jim Bourg/Reuters )","depth":3},{"id":2,"text":"The cynics","depth":8},{"id":3,"text":"- or , perhaps more precisely , the realists -","depth":8},{"id":4,"text":"believed","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"that the Democrats were playing for time in the hopes","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"of finding another accusation against Brett Kavanaugh .","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"The cynics were right .","depth":5},{"id":8,"text":"The New Yorker stooped to publish a shoddy story","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"alleging","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"that Kavanaugh exposed himself to a woman","depth":9},{"id":11,"text":"while he was at Yale .","depth":9},{"id":12,"text":"The alleged incident occurred at a drunken party","depth":7},{"id":13,"text":"when both were in their freshman year .","depth":7},{"id":14,"text":"What ' s extraordinary is that the woman","depth":11},{"id":15,"text":"making the charge ,","depth":11},{"id":16,"text":"a fellow Yale student","depth":11},{"id":17,"text":"named Deborah Ramirez ,","depth":11},{"id":18,"text":"admits","depth":9},{"id":19,"text":"that she hesitated to come forward","depth":9},{"id":20,"text":"because there were such large gaps in her memory .","depth":9},{"id":21,"text":"As the magazine puts it :","depth":9},{"id":22,"text":"\" In her initial conversations with The New Yorker , she was reluctant to characterize Kavanaugh ' s role in the alleged incident with certainty. \"","depth":10},{"id":23,"text":"She only decided to talk ,","depth":12},{"id":24,"text":"it says ,","depth":12},{"id":25,"text":"\" after six days","depth":12},{"id":26,"text":"of carefully assessing her memories","depth":13},{"id":27,"text":"and consulting with her attorney . \"","depth":13},{"id":28,"text":"Even after her new-found certainty","depth":10},{"id":29,"text":"- which happens to accord with her political interest as a Democrat -","depth":10},{"id":30,"text":"her story still contains gaps .","depth":9},{"id":31,"text":"She was drunk","depth":10},{"id":32,"text":"and didn ' t directly see","depth":11},{"id":33,"text":"that it was Kavanaugh who put his penis in front of her face","depth":12},{"id":34,"text":"when she was on the floor .","depth":12},{"id":35,"text":"She says","depth":11},{"id":36,"text":"she heard someone yell out","depth":13},{"id":37,"text":"that it was Kavanaugh who had done this ,","depth":13},{"id":38,"text":"and she saw him make a motion afterward","depth":13},{"id":39,"text":"that was consistent with pulling up his pants .","depth":13},{"id":40,"text":"So even she is making the charge as a matter of hearsay and interpretation .","depth":10},{"id":41,"text":"The only other corroboration is an unidentified classmate","depth":10},{"id":42,"text":"who tells the magazine","depth":11},{"id":43,"text":"that he heard of the incident afterwards","depth":11},{"id":44,"text":"- in other words , more hearsay .","depth":9},{"id":45,"text":"Otherwise ,","depth":9},{"id":46,"text":"the authors write ,","depth":11},{"id":47,"text":"\" The New Yorker has not confirmed with other eyewitnesses","depth":13},{"id":48,"text":"that Kavanaugh was present at the party ,","depth":13},{"id":49,"text":"\" a rather important lacuna","depth":13},{"id":50,"text":"if you are publishing a story","depth":14},{"id":51,"text":"that will contribute to an effort","depth":15},{"id":52,"text":"to destroy a man ' s reputation .","depth":15},{"id":53,"text":"( Where ' s William Shawn","depth":11},{"id":54,"text":"when you need him ? )","depth":11},{"id":55,"text":"Two male students","depth":11},{"id":56,"text":"identified by Ramirez","depth":12},{"id":57,"text":"as being present at the party","depth":12},{"id":58,"text":"said","depth":10},{"id":59,"text":"they had no recollection of any such incident .","depth":9},{"id":60,"text":"The New Yorker story comes on the heels of another blow to the credibility of Christine Blasey Ford ' s account .","depth":6},{"id":61,"text":"She has identified four other people","depth":8},{"id":62,"text":"who were present at the high-school party","depth":9},{"id":63,"text":"where Kavanaugh allegedly assaulted her as a teenager .","depth":9},{"id":64,"text":"All have denied it ,","depth":9},{"id":65,"text":"now including Leland Keyser ,","depth":10},{"id":66,"text":"who is a long-time friend of Ford ' s and a Democrat .","depth":10},{"id":67,"text":"She told the Judiciary Committee through her lawyer ,","depth":9},{"id":68,"text":"\" Simply put , Ms. Keyser does not know Mr. Kavanaugh","depth":10},{"id":69,"text":"and she has no recollection","depth":11},{"id":70,"text":"of ever being at a party or gathering","depth":12},{"id":71,"text":"where he was present , with , or without , Dr. Ford . \"","depth":12},{"id":72,"text":"Clearly , the opposition to Kavanaugh hopes","depth":6},{"id":73,"text":"that the two stories","depth":8},{"id":74,"text":"- with perhaps more on the way -","depth":8},{"id":75,"text":"will support each other","depth":8},{"id":76,"text":"despite their inherent weakness .","depth":8},{"id":77,"text":"If Democrats take down Kavanaugh on the basis of these charges ,","depth":5},{"id":78,"text":"they will have achieved the miraculous","depth":6},{"id":79,"text":"by stopping a Supreme Court nominee with two unproven and probably unprovable charges , in a smashing victory for garbage-pail politics .","depth":6},{"id":80,"text":"Brett Kavanaugh is an excellent jurist","depth":4},{"id":81,"text":"who has earned his sterling reputation over decades of public service .","depth":4},{"id":82,"text":"If his career is going to be ruined","depth":5},{"id":83,"text":"and his reputation besmirched ,","depth":5},{"id":84,"text":"it should require clear and convincing evidence .","depth":4},{"id":85,"text":"We are willing to follow the facts","depth":5},{"id":86,"text":"wherever they lead ,","depth":5},{"id":87,"text":"but so far , they lead only to the belief","depth":5},{"id":88,"text":"that this is a disgraceful episode","depth":6},{"id":89,"text":"that makes Borking look above-board and responsible by comparison .","depth":6},{"id":90,"text":"If Republicans surrender on the basis of what we know now ,","depth":4},{"id":91,"text":"they will face the fury of their own voters","depth":5},{"id":92,"text":"- and rightly so .","depth":5}],"relations":[{"parent":185,"left":172,"right":184,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":172,"left":94,"right":171,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":94,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":171,"left":151,"right":170,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":151,"left":99,"right":150,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":99,"left":98,"right":7,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":98,"left":96,"right":97,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":96,"left":95,"right":4,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":95,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"restatement","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":97,"left":5,"right":6,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":150,"left":104,"right":149,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":104,"left":102,"right":103,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":102,"left":8,"right":101,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":101,"left":9,"right":100,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":100,"left":10,"right":11,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":103,"left":12,"right":13,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":149,"left":120,"right":148,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":120,"left":110,"right":119,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":110,"left":108,"right":109,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":108,"left":107,"right":1